{"tid":1605531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（10.1和理非前哨戰）ig、Twitter圖海賀佢老母，有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T11:41:36.000Z","uid":79382,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6085bc0d4b31409be1860a09bd594634871acd6","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"聽日大壽正日當然係重頭戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係之前好多人話畫面好重要，<br />\n其實都有道理，不過而家和理非遊行嘅成本都好高，<br />\n好多人未必敢出，出咗都未必成功行到。<br />\n咁不如將呢個「畫面」搬上ig同Twitter？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqEkL5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqEkL5n.jpg&h=09b289e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖大家尋日應該見過，<br />\n如果<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今晚10點鐘</strong></span></span>，一人post一張上ig、Twitter，<br />\nhashtag埋 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#antichinazi</span></strong></span> 同 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#china</span></span></strong> （呢個重要，因為啲人未必識antichinazi，但10.1應該多人search China）<br />\n目標係啲人一搵支那嘅關鍵字，就會見到抗共嘅圖海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果喺Twitter<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>瘋狂like同retweet</strong></span></span>，<br />\n甚至有機會將antichinazi推上world trend <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，真係零成本，唔使出樣，唔使出門口，<br />\n撳兩個掣，1分鐘做完，有冇得諗？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9552aa7fb06805426b9dcc0312f657afe4b574","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39Qgjtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39Qgjtv.jpg&h=dd6139df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，聽日六/七區，遍地開花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd20e274012c25d503bf08a059ad137b5e3cb58","tid":1605531,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8089059c235dc33b7c2ae8c8af36399a9972fa00","tid":1605531,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"5365185d799d2127c670ac2187bb3872a4e93ce8","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:20:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75316869d1e2c861fa611d12d5746036c2408b14","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f790d042cc66968e5b65d7e425ff4e68a5a15783","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"何以"},{"pid":"6e1b79c01df3942202100c558800695307365b39","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f790d042cc66968e5b65d7e425ff4e68a5a15783","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"何以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"這土地"},{"pid":"09793627f9a1a90160be9fc02366bc114e3e151d","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e1b79c01df3942202100c558800695307365b39","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f790d042cc66968e5b65d7e425ff4e68a5a15783","tid":1605531,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30